                  <p>Tilføj så mange billeder du har lyst til, dog maks. 8</p>
                </div>
                <button id="uploadButton">Upload billeder</button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="figure">
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="line"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="content">
                <div class="text-box">
                  <h2>Giv os lidt informationer om annoncen, indtast kun rigtige informationer og vær præcis.</h2>
                  <form>
                    <label for="price"></label>
                    <input type="number" class="price" id="price" placeholder="Pris*" />
                  </form>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section id="section2"></section>
        <section id="section3"><p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Facere repellendus delectus aut adipisci distinctio! Accusamus odit, dolores fugit, nulla dignissimos nemo numquam dolorum delectus unde recusandae consequuntur a pariatur libero!</p></section>
